{% set version = "0.3" %}

package:
  name: pymesh2
  version: {{ version }}

  sha256: e1e1d6073144d2c8fba9d6df12f56ef92a65245db25e24c28b6abefa9bc65154

  skip: true  # [not (linux and py36)]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install --no-deps -vv --ignore-installed ./pymesh2-{{ version }}-cp36-cp36m-linux_x86_64.whl

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - scipy

    - pymesh  # [not linux]
